Program: Outlook
Title: From neo-Nazi to Christian pastor
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yqt2g
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 10 Oct 2012
The German neo-Nazi who found God in prison and is now training to become a pastor. Also, Finding Mercy: one woman's undercover search for a long-lost childhood friend in Zimbabwe. And the Burmese blogger who was sent to prison for criticising the government on the internet.